cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the task of extracting relevant pathological terms from radiology reports using various APIs and a DNN-based Named Entity Recognition model. This task involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
